main event: A businessman named Shull observed a self-luminous round object moving in a generally northerly direction in Ventura, California.
interesting points: The object was observed for approximately 2-3 minutes,The object was white in color and appeared to gain and lose altitude,The object made no sound and left no trail,Shull was the only witness to the sighting,The case was classified as UNIDENTIFIED despite possible explanations being considered.
witness description: Shull is a businessman, but no other biographical data is available.
